<p class="">It was the Secretary of State for War who was involved, not the Secretary of State for the Colonies. One should take into account the fact that information can be transmitted rapidly. I think we had better wait and see what the result of the report is.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
